The '''Moon Daggers''' were a gang organized by [[Myrkyssa Jelan]] in [[1479 DR]] shortly after she escaped her imprisonment in the [[mythal]] beneath [[Ravens Bluff]].{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|1414|5}}

The gang attempted to recover the [[Sarkonagael]] [[spellbook]] in the ruined [[dwarven]] city of [[Sarbreen]] beneath Ravens Bluff but were slightly slower than [[Jack Ravenwild]] and his hirelings, the [[Blue Wyverns]], who beat the Moon Daggers to the book.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|2833|8}}

Later, Myrkyssa and the Moon Daggers helped to defeat an attack by the [[slave|slaver]] [[Cailek Balathorp|Fetterfist]] and his [[drow]] allies on a noble revel.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|4263|13}}
